00:00:05,350 --> 00:00:10,710
greatest name of all times of flamenco dance...
弗拉門戈舞蹈史上最偉大的人

4
00:00:11,270 --> 00:00:12,990
Senora Feza.
塞諾拉·費紮

5
00:00:13,790 --> 00:00:15,750
- Olé. - Sure, Olé.
-奧萊！-當然，奧萊

6
00:00:16,190 --> 00:00:17,470
Do you think Nevra was convinced?
你認為內芙拉被說服了嗎？

7
00:00:18,350 --> 00:00:19,350
Absolutely.
絕對的

8
00:00:19,430 --> 00:00:22,390
So much for been convinced. She is following us.
真是太令人信服了  她正在跟蹤我們

9
00:00:25,230 --> 00:00:27,750
The three man who were killed...
被殺的三個人

10
00:00:27,870 --> 00:00:29,830
they were on the list in our website.
