What the hell do you think you're doing?
你以為你在做什麼？

14
00:00:51,550 --> 00:00:54,190
That's why the woman neither got raped nor she got married.
這就是那個女人既冇有被強姦也冇有結過婚的原因

15
00:00:54,230 --> 00:00:56,040
But we knew she was married. I decided to follow her to find out...
但是我們知道她已經結婚了  所以我決定去了解……

16
00:00:56,070 --> 00:00:58,790
where she was going and who was forcing her to lie.
她要去哪裏，誰在強迫她說謊

17
00:01:00,790 --> 00:01:02,190
That's when you came into the scene.
那時你就出現了

18
00:01:06,030 --> 00:01:09,630
- How did you find out? - I wanted to see the place.
-你怎麼知道的？-我想看看這個地方

19
00:01:10,470 --> 00:01:13,430
As you can see, the place has gone back in time.
如你所見，房子已經消失了

20
00:01:18,910 --> 00:01:19,910
Nevra Elmas.
內芙拉·埃爾瑪斯

21
00:01:21,510 --> 00:01:22,830
Mrs Nesrin's daughter.
內斯林夫人的女兒

22
00:01:24,150 --> 00:01:25,670
Don't call me on this number again.
不要再打這個電話給我

23
00:01:26,230 --> 00:01:28,390
In fact, it is better if you forget this number.
實際上，最好忘記這個號碼

24
00:01:36,070 --> 00:01:37,350
What do you want?
你想要什麼？

25
00:01:38,350 --> 00:01:40,510
Now, the honourable D.A...
現在，尊敬的檢察長

26
00:01:41,190 --> 00:01:43,150
who has been messing with my case and why?
誰一直在糾纏我的案子，為什麼？

27
00:01:43,470 --> 00:01:45,110
This is number one.
這是第一

28
00:01:45,310 --> 00:01:46,870
And the number two...
還有第二……

29
00:01:46,950 --> 00:01:50,550
who specifically reinstated the man to the case whom I removed?
誰讓菲魯茲回到案件調查中來的？

30
00:01:51,670 --> 00:01:54,350
Who is running this case? What's going on?
誰在處理這些事？怎麼回事？

31
00:02:05,150 --> 00:02:06,230
Nevra!
內芙拉！

32
00:02:10,390 --> 00:02:13,150
- Reyhan. - Who is Reyhan?
-雷漢-誰是雷漢？

33
00:03:01,910 --> 00:03:03,670
[Did you hide your gift?]
[你把禮物藏起來了嗎？]

34
00:03:06,830 --> 00:03:08,910
[Yes. What do you want from me?]
[是的，你想從我這裏得到什麼？]

35
00:03:10,990 --> 00:03:12,630
[To meet me.]
[見我]

36
00:03:14,790 --> 00:03:16,430
[When and where?]
[何時何地？]

37
00:03:16,750 --> 00:03:18,070
[Soon and nearby.]
[很快  就在附近]

38
00:03:20,990 --> 00:03:22,310
[How will I recognize you?]
[我怎麼知道是你？]

39
00:03:23,750 --> 00:03:26,150
[There'll be another gift in my hand.]
[我手裏還會有另一件禮物]

40
00:03:28,110 --> 00:03:29,310
[What is it?]
[它是什麼？]

41
00:05:07,230 --> 00:05:08,430
Deva!
德瓦！

42
00:05:10,310 --> 00:05:11,590
Grandad!
爺爺

43
00:05:11,710 --> 00:05:13,230
Turn that thing of.
把那個東西關掉

44
00:05:14,230 --> 00:05:16,510
Something really bad happened to me today, because of you.
今天因為你  我發生了一件很糟糕的事情

45
00:05:17,070 --> 00:05:18,070
Why? What happened?
怎麼了?

46
00:05:18,470 --> 00:05:20,080
What's done is done. None of your business.
木已成舟  不關你的事

47
00:05:20,110 --> 00:05:21,110
Dad?
爸？

48
00:05:21,310 --> 00:05:24,070
What's going on? Why are you shouting at the boy?
這是怎麼回事？為什麼朝他大喊？

49
00:05:24,590 --> 00:05:26,350
He put the car's logbook in a wrong place.
他把汽車的日誌放在其他的地方

50
00:05:26,470 --> 00:05:27,870
I wasted my morning looking for it.
我找了一早上

51
00:05:28,430 --> 00:05:31,270
Is that what it was? I thought something happened.
那是什麼大事嗎？我以為發生了什麼

52
00:05:32,550 --> 00:05:33,550
Did you find it anyway?
最後你找到了嗎？

53
00:05:34,190 --> 00:05:35,190
Yes, I did.
是的，我找到了

54
00:05:36,710 --> 00:05:37,710
But it was too late.
但為時已晚了

55
00:05:46,310 --> 00:05:47,630
- Thanks. - Thank you.
- 非常感謝- 非常感謝

56
00:05:50,030 --> 00:05:51,110
Did we find her?
我們找到她了嗎？

57
00:05:52,310 --> 00:05:54,510
I mean, is this the girl whom Tayyar raped?
我的意思是，這就是塔亞爾強奸的女孩嗎？

58
00:05:54,830 --> 00:05:55,830
I don't know.
我不知道

59
00:05:57,550 --> 00:05:59,150
But even if we found her, it is too late.
但是即使我們找到她，也為時已晚

60
00:06:00,070 --> 00:06:01,150
Much too late.
為時已晚

61
00:06:06,950 --> 00:06:08,150
Reyhan, wait!
雷漢，等等！

62
00:06:13,070 --> 00:06:16,030
My poor baby, how could you take your own life?
我可憐的孩子，你怎麼能結束自己的生命？

63
00:06:18,070 --> 00:06:19,270
She was still a baby.
她還是個孩子

64
00:06:19,710 --> 00:06:21,590
Don't you remember Reyhan, mum?
媽媽，你不記得雷漢嗎？

65
00:06:21,790 --> 00:06:23,990
No darling, I don't remember her.
親愛的，我不記得她了

66
00:06:25,510 --> 00:06:26,590
Was she your friend?
她是你的朋友嗎？

67
00:06:28,870 --> 00:06:30,190
We were classmates.
我們是同學

68
00:06:31,590 --> 00:06:34,310
But I erased almost every memory related to Kambura.
但是我幾乎抹掉了所有與坎佈拉相關的記憶

69
00:06:34,630 --> 00:06:35,830
I don't remember anything.
我什麼都不記得了

70
00:06:37,470 --> 00:06:40,870
But when I saw the photo I thought "I know this girl."
但是當我看到照片時，我以為“我認識這個女孩”

71
00:06:41,870 --> 00:06:43,070
"This is Reyhan."
“這是雷漢”

72
00:06:43,590 --> 00:06:45,230
She was slightly older than me.
她比我大一點

73
00:06:47,110 --> 00:06:49,270
That's right, she was 2 years older than me.
是的，她比我大2歲

74
00:06:51,590 --> 00:06:53,110
What else do you remember?
你還記得什麼？

75
00:07:02,510 --> 00:07:03,510
I don't know.
我不知道

76
00:07:04,030 --> 00:07:05,230
It is not very clear.
不太清楚

77
00:07:07,390 --> 00:07:11,870
I don't think Reyhan committing suicide is linked to Tayyar's death.
我不認為雷漢自殺與塔亞爾的死有關

78
00:07:13,630 --> 00:07:15,510
She committed suicide in 1996.
她於1996年自殺

79
00:07:15,710 --> 00:07:18,310
Tayyar died in 2008.There are 12 years in between.
塔亞爾於2008年過身，這之間存在12年的時間

80
00:07:20,510 --> 00:07:24,670
Whoever burned down Tayyar's house, be it Ufuk or somebody else...
燒毀塔亞爾房屋的人，無論是烏福克還是其他人

81
00:07:24,790 --> 00:07:27,830
wouldn't have waited 12 years to take Reyhan's revenge.
不會等12年才報仇

82
00:07:29,470 --> 00:07:32,790
Anyway, it is not yet clear why Reyhan had committed suicide.
無論如何，目前尚不清楚為什麼雷漢自殺

83
00:07:36,070 --> 00:07:38,270
She committed suicide 2 years after we left the town.
我們離開小鎮兩年後，她自殺了

84
00:07:40,230 --> 00:07:41,790
How old was she at the time?
她當時幾歲？

85
00:07:43,390 --> 00:07:44,590
She was 2 years older than me.
她比我大2歲

86
00:07:44,710 --> 00:07:46,150
That makes her 14.
那讓她14歲

87
00:07:49,630 --> 00:07:51,470
Why would she do such a thing?
她為什麼要這樣做？

88
00:07:53,030 --> 00:07:56,950
There are 11 cases of female suicide in the last 15 years.
最近15年有11例女性自殺案

89
00:07:57,590 --> 00:08:00,870
The dates are closer to the time when Tayyar was murdered.
日期更接近塔亞爾被謀殺的時間

90
00:08:01,870 --> 00:08:05,150
If there is a case of rape it's got be one of them.
如果發生強奸案，應該是這其中一例

91
00:08:06,110 --> 00:08:09,190
I think we should start by digging into these files.
我認為我們應該首先研究這些文件

92
00:08:10,830 --> 00:08:12,350
I don't know any of these girls.
這些女孩我都不認識

93
00:08:18,670 --> 00:08:19,870
Excuse me.
不好意思

94
00:08:22,270 --> 00:08:23,270
Hello?
餵？

95
00:08:24,670 --> 00:08:27,510
O, K, let's assume that this case is directly linked to you.
好了，讓我們假設這個案例直接與你相關

96
00:08:28,830 --> 00:08:32,950
You must know the victim or the killer, or whatever you want to call them.
你一定認識受害者或兇手

97
00:08:33,390 --> 00:08:36,230
So, it may come to you later, just like you remembered Reyhan.
所以，可能你過後就記起來了，就像你記得雷漢

98
00:08:48,670 --> 00:08:50,550
Just tell me when and where.
告訴我何時何地

99
00:08:55,430 --> 00:08:57,070
Don't worry, no one will know.
別擔心，冇人會知道

100
00:09:00,150 --> 00:09:02,110
Why don't you try to trust me?
你為什麼不相信我？

101
00:09:02,990 --> 00:09:05,910
If you ask me, this Reyhan case is waste of time.
如果你問我，這件雷汗案是浪費時間

102
00:09:09,110 --> 00:09:10,390
Just one more day.
再給我一天時間

103
00:09:12,270 --> 00:09:14,550
If I don't get a break I'll go back to Istanbul.
如果我冇有任何進展就回伊斯坦佈爾

104
00:09:14,790 --> 00:09:18,030
O.K, whatever you say. Meanwhile I'll go through the files.
好的，你請便吧，與此同時我來調查這些文件

105
00:09:19,910 --> 00:09:21,430
O.K, I've got to go.
好  我先走了

106
00:09:42,470 --> 00:09:43,670
How are you doing?
你好嗎？

107
00:09:44,990 --> 00:09:46,190
I don't know.
我不知道

108
00:09:49,710 --> 00:09:51,110
Where are you going to start?
你要從哪裏開始？

109
00:09:54,270 --> 00:09:56,790
I'll check her house first...
我先去看看她的房子

110
00:09:56,910 --> 00:09:58,870
and the place I remember her from.
還有我記得她的地方

111
00:09:59,550 --> 00:10:00,830
The school.
學校

112
00:10:01,830 --> 00:10:04,990
My mum knows our teacher. He settled here after he got retired.
我媽媽認識我們的老師  他退休後在這裏定居

113
00:10:05,590 --> 00:10:06,990
I'll talk to him.
我會跟他談談

114
00:10:08,310 --> 00:10:09,590
I don't know.
我不知道

115
00:10:09,830 --> 00:10:12,030
How about you? Will you go back to Istanbul?
你呢？你會回到伊斯坦佈爾嗎？

116
00:10:14,110 --> 00:10:16,830
Actually, now that I am here, I can ask your mother's permission...
其實，現在我就在這裏，我想請你媽媽同意……

117
00:10:16,910 --> 00:10:18,030
to marry you.
讓你嫁給我

118
00:10:18,670 --> 00:10:20,950
But she'd probably ask what I do for a living.
但她可能會問我是做什麼工作的

119
00:10:21,630 --> 00:10:26,110
And I say to her "I am a foot soldier in the army of unemployed journalists".
我對她說：“我是失業記者大軍中的一名步兵”

120
00:10:28,950 --> 00:10:32,230
That's why I should go back to Istanbul and return when I get a job.
這就是為什麼我應該先回到伊斯坦佈爾找到工作後再來

121
00:10:53,110 --> 00:10:56,510
- Are you alright dad? - So so.
-爸爸你還好嗎？-還行

122
00:11:01,190 --> 00:11:03,950
Are you still upset about that logbook thing?
你還在對日誌的事情生氣嗎？

123
00:11:04,590 --> 00:11:06,310
No, no. It doesn't matter anymore.
不，不，已經無所謂了

124
00:11:06,750 --> 00:11:08,510
- I am sorry. - Yeah, O.K.
-對不起  -好的，好的

125
00:11:09,950 --> 00:11:12,790
You used to do the same to me when I was little, remember?
你小時候對我也這樣，還記得嗎？

126
00:11:14,310 --> 00:11:17,030
You used to put me through hell for the smallest thing.
你曾經為了很小的事情就對我大喊大叫

127
00:11:17,230 --> 00:11:18,430
Nothing has changed.
什麼也冇有變

128
00:11:20,310 --> 00:11:21,830
Once I broke the video.
有一次我弄壞了電視

129
00:11:22,390 --> 00:11:25,550
If it wasn't for my mum he would've kicked me out.
如果不是我媽媽的話我會被我趕出去

130
00:11:26,190 --> 00:11:27,630
He was so mad.
他很生氣

131
00:11:28,150 --> 00:11:30,030
It was just a video, a piece of machinery.
這隻是一臺電視，一臺機器

132
00:11:30,350 --> 00:11:32,720
I had the right to be mad. I told you not to mess around with it.
我有權生氣  我告訴過你不要胡鬨

133
00:11:32,750 --> 00:11:34,070
We'd only just bought it.
我們新買的

134
00:11:34,390 --> 00:11:36,880
I wanted to enjoy a good movie only to find out that it wasn't working.
我想好好看一部電影，但發現它壞了

135
00:11:36,910 --> 00:11:38,870
I'm  only just begun to pay the instalments.
我才剛開始分期付款

136
00:11:39,070 --> 00:11:40,830
Do you know how much it cost to get it fixed?
你知道修複它需要花多少錢嗎？

137
00:11:41,750 --> 00:11:44,070
You have such a good memory. It is scary.
你的記憶力真好

138
00:11:45,350 --> 00:11:47,870
You probably still remember what the movie was.
你可能還記得當時要看的電影是什麼

139
00:11:48,070 --> 00:11:49,310
Of course I do.
我當然記得了

140
00:11:49,390 --> 00:11:51,590
Kramer vs Kramer. Of course I remember.
克萊默vs克萊默  我當然記得

141
00:11:51,790 --> 00:11:53,230
How do you remember all this?
你是怎麼記得住所有這些的？

142
00:11:53,550 --> 00:11:54,630
I never forget.
我永遠不會忘記

143
00:11:55,750 --> 00:11:58,030
Now I remember. I remember the old.
現在我還記得  我記得過去的所有事

144
00:12:01,390 --> 00:12:05,230
Now there is even a better movie out. Beyo?lu vs Beyo?lu.
現在有更好的電影了  貝尤魯vs貝尤魯

145
00:12:07,630 --> 00:12:09,350
What do you think? Is it nice?
你覺得怎麼樣？

146
00:12:13,070 --> 00:12:16,350
I am so glad that I broke that video. Well done to me.
我很高興我弄壞了電視  我真棒

147
00:12:17,670 --> 00:12:19,430
- I am off. - Where to?
-我走了-去哪裏？

148
00:12:20,070 --> 00:12:22,030
I am going on a vacation with Miss Nükhet.
我要和努赫特小姐一起渡假

149
00:12:23,790 --> 00:12:25,390
Going on a vacation with Nükhet?
和努赫特一起度假嗎？

150
00:12:26,390 --> 00:12:28,470
What is he going to do with that woman?
他跟那個女人有什麼關係？

151
00:12:28,910 --> 00:12:30,870
"That woman" loves me.
“那個女人”愛我

152
00:12:31,950 --> 00:12:34,270
Does she know you well enough to love you?
她對你的了解足夠使她愛你嗎？

153
00:12:34,590 --> 00:12:37,110
Because it's easy to love someone whom you don't really know.
因為愛一個你不認識的人很容易

154
00:12:37,310 --> 00:12:39,190
I both know and love you.
我既了解又愛你

155
00:12:39,390 --> 00:12:41,150
Let's see if she can do the same.
讓我們看看她是否也能做到

156
00:12:42,550 --> 00:12:44,390
What is he going to do with Nükhet on vacation?
他在旅行時會與努赫特做什麼？

157
00:12:44,830 --> 00:12:46,510
We'll make love all night.
我們會整夜做愛

158
00:12:47,150 --> 00:12:48,470
What did he say?
他說什麼？

159
00:13:11,870 --> 00:13:14,630
Do you know...
你知道嗎

160
00:13:14,710 --> 00:13:18,110
one day, they'll put us in jars just like these...
有一天，他們會把我們放在這樣的罐子裏

161
00:13:18,310 --> 00:13:22,270
and scientists will say "there used be a species called "human"...
科學家會說“曾經有種叫做’人類‘的物種“

162
00:13:22,350 --> 00:13:23,910
but now it's extinct.
但是現在已經滅絕了

163
00:13:24,670 --> 00:13:26,070
It became obsolete.
過時了

164
00:13:30,470 --> 00:13:32,750
We may have nothing left to be put in jars.
我們可能冇什麼可放入罐子裏了

165
00:13:34,510 --> 00:13:39,270
The way we're going, the human race will wipe itself off the history.
我們前進的道路上，人類將把自己從曆史中抹掉

166
00:13:41,910 --> 00:13:43,230
That's correct too.
說的也對

167
00:13:43,430 --> 00:13:45,510
For once, we are on the same side.
我們第一次達成共識

168
00:13:47,070 --> 00:13:49,110
First of all, thanks for coming Ate?.
