When you called me this morning to tell me that...
當你今天早上給我打電話告訴我……

268
00:19:21,750 --> 00:19:24,150
we are leaving right away. That was the real surprise.
我們馬上出發  那才是真正的驚喜

269
00:19:24,710 --> 00:19:26,590
You caught me off guard.
你讓我措手不及

270
