00:25:23,630 --> 00:25:26,590
You never know what goes on in someone's head.
你永遠不知道別人腦子裏想的是什麼

348
00:25:30,630 --> 00:25:32,910
Binnaz, come over here. Sit with us darling.
賓納茲，過來  和我們坐一會吧

349
00:25:33,150 --> 00:25:35,630
No thanks. I'll be inside.
不用了，我進屋去

350
00:25:38,590 --> 00:25:40,230
She was really talented.
她真的很有才華

351
00:25:41,110 --> 00:25:43,390
She used to write great compositions.
她曾經寫過很好的作品

352
00:25:45,390 --> 00:25:48,870
She was a late starter at school. But she was really smart.
她在學校起步較晚，但是她很聰明

353
00:25:49,950 --> 00:25:52,710
She was very smart. She was like a diamond.
她很聰明  就像一顆鑽石

354
00:25:54,230 --> 00:25:55,430
And talented.
有才華

355
00:25:56,950 --> 00:25:58,790
She only had a granny.
她的親人隻有一個奶奶

356
00:26:00,670 --> 00:26:02,190
She had nobody else.
冇有其他了

357
00:26:04,270 --> 00:26:06,110
And she passed away.
並且她奶奶也過身了

358
00:26:07,750 --> 00:26:10,030
Well sir...
先生……

359
00:26:10,110 --> 00:26:12,550
as far as you can remember...
盡可能回想一下……

360
00:26:12,630 --> 00:26:15,350
do you think something might've happened to Reyhan...
你覺得雷漢有發生什麼事嗎？

361
00:26:15,470 --> 00:26:16,790
after we left town?
在我們離開城鎮後？

362
00:26:17,870 --> 00:26:19,950
No, I don't think so.
不，我認為冇有

363
00:26:21,430 --> 00:26:24,510
As far as I remember, there was no wrong doing.
據我所知，冇有任何不對的事情

364
00:26:25,910 --> 00:26:29,190
But she was missing school as of late.
但是她那時經常不來學校

365
00:26:32,790 --> 00:26:34,670
She was there one day but not the next.
她一天在那裏，但第二天卻不在

366
00:26:37,830 --> 00:26:41,190
Her file says cause of death is suicide due to heavy depression.
她的檔案中說，由於嚴重抑鬱而導緻自殺是死亡的原因

367
00:26:43,310 --> 00:26:45,590
Have you noticed anything? Was she depressed?
你有註意到嗎？她沮喪嗎？

368
00:26:48,550 --> 00:26:53,550
As far as I remember, Reyhan was a cheerful girl with a big smile.
我記得，雷漢是一個開朗的女孩，笑容燦爛

369
00:26:57,630 --> 00:27:01,310
But it is not possible to know what's been happening deep inside.
但不知道她內心深處發生了什麼

370
00:27:08,310 --> 00:27:09,630
Sir, can I use the toilet?
先生，我可以上廁所嗎？

371
00:27:11,030 --> 00:27:13,550
What is this? Is this how I trained you?
這是什麼？我是這麼教你的嗎？

372
00:27:15,510 --> 00:27:17,830
You have to raise your hand and ask for permission first.
你必須舉手並先徵得許可

373
00:27:24,350 --> 00:27:25,670
I was joking.
我在開玩笑

374
00:27:26,190 --> 00:27:28,510
Nevra, my sweetheart. I was only joking.
內芙拉，我隻是在開玩笑

375
00:27:28,950 --> 00:27:31,790
Go ahead. Binnaz will show you the way.
去吧，賓納茲會帶你去

376
00:27:46,510 --> 00:27:47,710
Damn! I'll be late.
該死  我要遲到了

377
00:28:13,070 --> 00:28:14,470
Did you know Reyhan?
你認識雷漢嗎

378
00:28:15,030 --> 00:28:16,030
No.
不認識

379
00:28:16,750 --> 00:28:18,950
I am not from around here anyway.
我不是來自這裏的

380
00:28:19,590 --> 00:28:20,870
I've come from the village.
我來自鄉村

381
00:28:22,830 --> 00:28:24,550
When did you come to Kambura?
你什麼時候來坎佈拉的？

382
00:28:25,750 --> 00:28:27,950
After I got married.
我結婚後

383
00:28:28,070 --> 00:28:30,230
I was around 15 years old. That's how I ended up here.
我當時大約15歲，最後就這樣了

384
00:28:30,470 --> 00:28:31,550
Fifteen?
十五歲？

385
00:28:34,510 --> 00:28:36,350
How old was Mr Tahsin at the time?
當時塔欣先生多大了？

386
00:28:37,790 --> 00:28:38,990
In his fifties.
五十多歲

387
00:28:40,630 --> 00:28:41,630
I see.
我知道了

388
00:28:43,150 --> 00:28:44,150
Thanks.
謝謝

389
00:28:46,630 --> 00:28:48,590
Do you have something to tell me Binnaz?
你有話要告訴我嗎？賓納茲

390
00:28:51,870 --> 00:28:54,270
I don't know that girl, Reyhan, but...!
我不認識那個女孩，雷漢，但是！

391
00:28:56,670 --> 00:28:57,670
Binnaz!
賓納茲！

392
00:29:00,150 --> 00:29:01,590
Can you pour me some tea?
你可以給我倒茶嗎？

393
00:29:03,550 --> 00:29:06,510
I was new around here. May be only a year.
我在這裏很陌生  可能隻有一年

394
00:29:07,150 --> 00:29:09,230
I heard that a girl took her own life.
聽說一個女孩子自殺了

395
00:29:09,670 --> 00:29:12,270
God almighty! Can't she hear me?
天啊！她聽不到我說話嗎？

396
00:29:13,390 --> 00:29:16,110
Binnaz! I asked you to fill my glass.
賓納茲  我讓你來給我倒茶

397
00:29:17,430 --> 00:29:18,430
Binnaz!
賓納茲！

398
00:29:18,950 --> 00:29:23,390
One day, while he was at school a woman popped-by.
有一天，當他在學校的時候，一個女人突然出現了

399
00:29:24,150 --> 00:29:26,110
She said she was Reyhan's granny.
她說她是雷漢的奶奶

400
00:29:27,750 --> 00:29:30,670
She said she found a notebook hidden inside her pillow.
她說她在枕頭裏發現了一個筆記本

401
00:29:30,790 --> 00:29:32,430
She said "she wrote down everything here".
她說：“她在這裏寫下了一切”

402
00:29:32,550 --> 00:29:34,630
"This may reveal clues as to why she killed herself".
“這可能揭示出她為何自殺的線索”

403
00:29:34,830 --> 00:29:36,310
Why did she bring the notebook to you?
她為什麼把筆記本帶給你？

404
00:29:36,350 --> 00:29:37,350
Binnaz!
賓納茲！

405
00:29:38,310 --> 00:29:39,630
Why did she bring it to you?
她為什麼把它帶給你？

406
00:29:40,310 --> 00:29:41,510
She was illiterate.
因為她是文盲

407
00:29:42,710 --> 00:29:45,310
She said "give this to the teacher, he'd know what to do with it".
她說：“把這個交給老師，他會知道該怎麼做的”

408
00:29:46,070 --> 00:29:47,070
And what did you do?
那你做了什麼？

409
00:29:47,630 --> 00:29:48,630
Binnaz!
賓納茲！

410
00:29:53,190 --> 00:29:55,590
I didn't do anything. I just took a quick glance.
我什麼也冇做我隻是看了一眼

411
00:29:56,670 --> 00:29:57,670
Then?
然後？

412
00:29:59,310 --> 00:30:03,310
I gave it back to her and told her to take it to the police station.
我把筆記本還給她，叫她去派出所

413
00:30:04,830 --> 00:30:06,030
She said she already did.
她說她已經去了

414
00:30:06,470 --> 00:30:10,190
But the police had sent her away saying that the case is already closed.
但是警察讓她回去，說案件已經結案了

415
00:30:12,910 --> 00:30:14,670
I told her to go to the courthouse.
我叫她去法院

416
00:30:18,470 --> 00:30:21,550
- What was in the notebook? - I don't know.
-筆記本裏有什麼？-我不知道

417
00:30:23,950 --> 00:30:25,910
I was illiterate at the time too.
我當時也是文盲

418
00:30:30,070 --> 00:30:32,350
Why did you tell her to take it to the courthouse...
你為什麼叫她去法院

419
00:30:32,470 --> 00:30:34,150
instead of handing it over to Mr.Tahsin?
而不是將其移交給塔欣先生？

420
00:30:34,550 --> 00:30:36,680
I wasn't about to give the poor girl's notebook to a man...
我不想把那個可憐女孩的筆記本

421
00:30:36,710 --> 00:30:38,590
who took a child as a wife.
給那個把孩子當成妻子的男人

422
00:30:41,870 --> 00:30:43,950
He loves me. We'll get married.
他愛我，我們要結婚了

423
00:30:44,390 --> 00:30:45,470
I'll be a bride.
我要做新娘了

424
00:30:59,510 --> 00:31:01,990
You two have been here for ages.
你們在這裏很久了

425
00:31:04,390 --> 00:31:07,230
I have been asking you to pour me a cup of tea.
我一直在叫你給我倒茶

426
00:31:08,110 --> 00:31:09,950
You wouldn't have known if I died.
我死了你都不知道

427
00:32:20,510 --> 00:32:21,710
S... it!
該死！

428
00:32:47,910 --> 00:32:49,310
This is Hamza.
我是哈姆紮

429
00:32:49,870 --> 00:32:51,950
I am Nevra, the deputy chief.
我是內芙拉  副警長

430
00:32:53,230 --> 00:32:55,750
I sure recognize you. How can I not, anyway?
我當然記得你

431
00:32:55,950 --> 00:32:58,150
How could you forget the one who put you away?
怎麼會忘記那個把我抓回來的人呢？

432
00:32:59,910 --> 00:33:01,310
What do you want this time?
這次你想要什麼？

433
00:33:01,990 --> 00:33:05,550
Has your brother Tayyar ever mentioned a girl named Reyhan?
你的兄弟塔亞爾提到過一個叫雷漢的女孩嗎？

434
00:33:07,230 --> 00:33:09,950
A 14 year old from Kambura. Reyhan.
來自坎佈拉的14歲女孩 雷漢

435
00:33:15,190 --> 00:33:17,710
-Can you hear me Hamza? -Yes, I can.
-你能聽到我說話嗎？哈姆紮？-能

436
00:33:19,350 --> 00:33:20,950
Did you say Reyhan?
你是說雷漢嗎？

437
00:33:21,750 --> 00:33:22,830
Yes, Reyhan.
是的，雷漢

438
00:33:25,030 --> 00:33:26,550
What's in it for me?
對我有什麼好處？

439
00:33:27,950 --> 00:33:30,350
- Do you know the girl? - I don't.
-你認識那個女孩嗎？-我不認識

440
00:33:30,790 --> 00:33:32,750
But let's say, I heard the name.
但是，假設我聽過這個名字

441
00:33:33,110 --> 00:33:35,270
What can you do for me?
你能為我做什麼？

442
00:33:36,710 --> 00:33:41,190
I tell you what I'll do, I'll come over there, lock you in solitary confinement...
我告訴你我會做什麼，我會過去你那，把你關在單獨的牢房裏

443
00:33:41,390 --> 00:33:43,590
and throw away the key. How about that?
然後把鎖匙讓掉  怎麼樣？

444
00:33:44,790 --> 00:33:46,510
You have such a quick temper, sis.
小姐姐你脾氣真大

445
00:33:48,350 --> 00:33:49,990
Woman with a short fuse.
脾氣暴躁的女人

446
00:33:51,070 --> 00:33:53,270
Look, I don't know much about this Reyhan girl.
聽著，我對這個叫雷漢的女孩不太了解

447
00:33:54,110 --> 00:33:56,550
This is the first time I hear the name after a long time.
這是我很久以來第一次聽到這個名字

448
00:33:57,070 --> 00:33:58,710
But now, I remember. 
但是現在，我想起來了

449
00:33:58,830 --> 00:34:01,350
Tayyar kept repeatingher name when he was stoned.
塔亞爾醉酒時一直重複她的名字

450
00:34:02,110 --> 00:34:05,910
When we asked about the girl he used to say things like...
當我們問起女孩時，他曾經說過類似……

451
00:34:06,030 --> 00:34:07,910
"poor girl, they wasted her".
“可憐的女孩，他們糟蹋了她”這樣的話

452
00:34:09,950 --> 00:34:14,710
We used to ask him after he sobered up but he couldn't remember anything.
他醒酒後，我們也問過他，但他不記得了

453
00:34:17,910 --> 00:34:21,630
Perhaps he remembered but avoided the subject with us.
也許他記得，但是閉口不談

454
00:34:22,710 --> 00:34:24,430
Why didn't you tell me anything?
你怎麼不告訴我？

455
00:34:24,990 --> 00:34:27,070
When I've asked you if Tayyar raped anyone...
當我問你泰雅是否強奸了任何人的時候……

456
00:34:27,310 --> 00:34:28,830
why didn't you mention Reyhan?
你為什麼不提雷漢？

457
00:34:30,470 --> 00:34:32,830
You are so gullible sis.
你好傻啊

458
00:34:34,710 --> 00:34:37,190
Tayyar was an alcoholic. He was stoned.
塔亞爾是一個酒鬼  他喝醉了

459
00:34:38,310 --> 00:34:40,910
He used to say "they wasted her", not "I wasted her".
他曾經說的是“他們浪費了她”，而不是“我浪費了她”

460
00:34:41,910 --> 00:34:44,310
I'll tell you what...
我告訴你……

461
00:34:44,510 --> 00:34:48,230
a drunken man can do anything except one thing...
一個喝醉的男人可以做任何事情，但隻有一件事不能做……

462
00:34:49,310 --> 00:34:50,750
he can't lie.
他不能撒謊

463
00:34:52,270 --> 00:34:54,990
If he got up to no good he would've told us.
如果是他做的，他會告訴我們

464
00:34:56,870 --> 00:34:58,510
It means that somebody else did it.
這說明是別人做的

465
00:35:10,190 --> 00:35:11,350
So, what is it?
那算什麼啊？

466
00:35:15,070 --> 00:35:17,710
The girl has gone and the case is closed, isn't it?
女孩死了，也已經結案了，不是嗎？

467
00:35:19,990 --> 00:35:21,390
Keep quiet Tayyar.
保持安靜  塔亞爾

468
00:35:23,150 --> 00:35:24,790
Keep quiet for what?
為什麼要安靜？

469
00:35:29,030 --> 00:35:30,790
She was wasted in broad day-light.
她在光天化日下被糟蹋了

470
00:35:32,750 --> 00:35:34,390
Poor Reyhan got wasted.
可憐的雷漢被人糟蹋了

471
00:35:38,110 --> 00:35:39,190
Shut up!
閉嘴！

472
00:35:41,470 --> 00:35:42,910
Do you call yourselves men?
你算什麼男人？

473
00:35:45,070 --> 00:35:47,150
What did you want from the poor girl?
你想從那個可憐的女孩那裏得到什麼？

474
00:36:00,350 --> 00:36:01,430
I am listening.
我聽著呢

475
00:36:01,670 --> 00:36:04,590
Sir, this plate is no longer registered.
先生，這個車牌已經登出了

476
00:36:04,710 --> 00:36:05,710
What do you mean?
什麼意思？

477
00:36:06,030 --> 00:36:10,150
It was dropped from the system in 1998 and the vehicle was scrapped.
它在1998年從係統中刪除，車輛報廢

478
00:36:17,390 --> 00:36:18,390
I see.
我知道了

479
00:36:25,110 --> 00:36:26,990
- Here is your coffee. - Thanks mum.
-這是你的咖啡-謝謝媽媽

480
00:36:34,510 --> 00:36:36,270
Mum...
媽媽

481
00:36:37,030 --> 00:36:39,670
I think really bad things happened here.
我覺得這裏真的發生了壞事

482
00:36:40,630 --> 00:36:42,590
Do you mean the burned house?
你是說被燒毀的房子嗎？

483
00:36:43,910 --> 00:36:45,990
No, not that. I mean Reyhan.
不，不是  我是說雷漢

484
00:36:47,070 --> 00:36:49,830
I think some people did very bad things to her.
我覺得有人對她做了壞事

485
00:36:51,350 --> 00:36:54,070
- What are you talking about? - I don't know.
-你在說什麼？-我不知道

486
00:36:56,790 --> 00:36:59,630
But whatever happened, people of Kambura are responsible.
但是不管發生什麼事，坎佈拉人都有責任

487
00:37:06,870 --> 00:37:08,270
Why are you laughing?
你笑什麼？

488
00:37:08,590 --> 00:37:10,550
What's going on? What are you doing?
怎麼了？你在做什麼？

489
00:37:11,310 --> 00:37:13,270
Do you know someone called Reyhan?
你認識叫雷漢的人嗎？

490
00:37:13,830 --> 00:37:15,670
- Who, who did you say? - Reyhan.
-誰，你說誰？-雷漢

491
00:37:16,550 --> 00:37:18,190
- Nevra's schoolmate. - Mum!
-內夫拉的同學-媽媽！

492
00:37:18,510 --> 00:37:21,150
The girl who committed suicide when she was 14.
14歲時自殺的女孩

493
00:37:21,670 --> 00:37:24,190
I swear, I don't know her. How would I know her anyway?
我發誓，我不認識她，我怎麼會認識她？

494
00:37:25,390 --> 00:37:27,790
Look, if you're hiding anything...!
聽著，如果你隱瞞了什麼……！

495
00:37:28,470 --> 00:37:31,390
Mum, calm down. Come here.
媽媽  冷靜點  過來

496
00:37:34,590 --> 00:37:36,110
- God almighty. - Calm down.
-天啊-冷靜

497
00:37:37,310 --> 00:37:38,310
Sit down.
坐下

498
00:37:44,270 --> 00:37:45,510
Uncle Selim...
塞利姆叔叔

499
00:37:47,910 --> 00:37:49,870
you know my friend, Reyhan...
你知道我的朋友雷漢……

500
00:37:51,070 --> 00:37:53,230
something really bad happened to her...
她真的發生了什麼壞事

501
00:37:53,470 --> 00:37:54,750
here in Kambura.
就在坎佈拉

502
00:37:55,830 --> 00:37:58,350
I am not too sure...
我不太確定

503
00:37:58,430 --> 00:38:02,470
but you know the killer who picks victims from Kambura...
但是你知道兇手現在從坎佈拉挑選受害者……

504
00:38:02,710 --> 00:38:05,110
I think he kills the ones who did evil to Reyhan.
我認為他是在殺那些對雷漢犯下邪惡罪行的人

505
00:38:05,550 --> 00:38:09,230
If you know anything about this or have an idea...
如果你對此有任何想法……

506
00:38:09,350 --> 00:38:11,550
please tell me. Don't be afraid.
請告訴我  不要害怕

507
00:38:14,910 --> 00:38:17,870
If you know anything but not telling me, that's when you should be afraid.
如果你什麼都知道但不告訴我，那你才應該感到害怕

508
00:38:18,110 --> 00:38:19,990
Because the killer will eventually find you too.
因為兇手最終也會找到你

509
00:38:20,070 --> 00:38:24,230
I told you, I haven't done anything. I only threw a small piece of stone.
我告訴過你，我什麼都冇做我隻扔了一小塊石頭

510
00:38:34,030 --> 00:38:36,110
Look here, you b... stard!
看著我  你這個畜生！

511
00:38:36,990 --> 00:38:38,510
Just spill the beans.
快說！

512
00:38:56,070 --> 00:39:00,230
You said he was having dreams about it...
你說過他是出現幻覺了……

513
00:39:00,430 --> 00:39:05,670
but thinking it was real because he was avoiding his medication.
但以為是真實發生的，因為他冇吃藥

514
00:39:07,750 --> 00:39:08,830
Was it worth it?
值得嗎？

515
00:39:09,710 --> 00:39:11,790
Was it worth you hiding it from me?
值得你嚮我隱瞞嗎？

516
00:39:12,230 --> 00:39:15,270
What did you think you were hiding? This?
你以為你隱藏了什麼？

517
00:39:16,710 --> 00:39:19,230
That you had a husband who lynched people.
你的丈夫用私刑殺人

518
00:39:22,510 --> 00:39:23,710
What good did that do?
那有什麼好處？

519
00:39:25,670 --> 00:39:28,270
You don't trust him tiny bit.
你一點都不相信他

520
00:39:28,350 --> 00:39:32,310
So much so that you belive he would do something to 14 year old girl.
以至於你相信他會對14歲的女孩做什麼事情

521
00:39:32,430 --> 00:39:34,390
And you even asked him.
你甚至直接問他……

522
00:39:40,710 --> 00:39:41,790
Mum!
媽！

523
00:39:46,830 --> 00:39:47,830
Why?
為什麼？

524
00:39:50,230 --> 00:39:51,950
Why have you become the woman you are?
你為什麼要成為那樣的女人？

525
00:39:52,190 --> 00:39:53,590
Why have such a life?
為什麼要過這樣的生活？

526
00:39:56,310 --> 00:39:58,390
I don't know any other life.
我什麼都不知道

527
00:40:00,150 --> 00:40:05,270
All I knew "Stand on your own feet, be independent, be strong..."
我所知道的“立足，獨立，堅強”

528
00:40:05,390 --> 00:40:07,590
you are an orphan".
”你是一個孤兒”

529
00:40:11,830 --> 00:40:14,030
"You have a deceased husband".
“你有一個已故的丈夫”

530
00:40:15,750 --> 00:40:18,270
"And a little girl in your arms".
“還有一個小女孩在你的懷裏”

531
00:40:21,430 --> 00:40:23,830
Don't ever fall. But how can you not?
永遠不要跌倒  但是你怎麼能不跌倒呢？

532
00:40:25,470 --> 00:40:27,950
You are young, working...
你還年輕……

533
00:40:28,190 --> 00:40:30,150
trying to make a living.
要想辦法謀生

534
00:40:31,550 --> 00:40:33,750
But you are not a man.
但是你不是一個男人

535
00:40:35,470 --> 00:40:36,470
You are a woman.
你是一個女人

536
00:40:40,590 --> 00:40:46,190
Wish you knew how you used to look at me when I held you in my arms.
希望你知道當我抱著你時你看我的眼神

537
00:40:50,870 --> 00:40:52,950
I was frightened of this world Nevra.
我被這個世界嚇壞了  內芙拉

538
00:40:55,030 --> 00:40:57,430
You have to hold on to a man.
你必須要依靠一個男人

539
00:40:59,950 --> 00:41:03,110
While trying to find the right one...
當我試圖找到一個合適的人時……

540
00:41:03,990 --> 00:41:06,070
I myself became a man.
我自己成為了一個男人

541
00:41:07,870 --> 00:41:09,270
I turned into a man.
我變成了男人

542
00:41:11,910 --> 00:41:14,630
When you asked me...
當你問我……

543
00:41:14,750 --> 00:41:17,590
why I hid it from you...
為什麼我嚮你隱瞞

544
00:41:17,710 --> 00:41:20,310
I was afraid to be left on my own...
我怕自己一個人呆著

545
00:41:20,430 --> 00:41:22,950
if they took Selim away.
如果他們把塞利姆帶走

546
00:41:28,190 --> 00:41:30,790
I was scared of being on my own.
我害怕獨自一人

547
00:41:32,990 --> 00:41:35,710
I always took cover behind men.
我總是躲在男人後麵

548
00:41:40,430 --> 00:41:45,990
In order to avoid being alone and being labelled "whore".
為了避免獨自一人而被貼上“妓女”的標簽

549
00:41:54,150 --> 00:41:55,350
But you weren't alone.
但是你並不孤單

550
00:41:56,630 --> 00:41:57,750
You had me.
你還有我

551
00:41:58,270 --> 00:41:59,830
And you still have.
一直都是

552
00:42:02,550 --> 00:42:04,070
Why were you so scared?
你怎麼這麼害怕

553
00:42:07,350 --> 00:42:10,070
My little darling...
我的小寶貝……

554
00:42:10,190 --> 00:42:13,790
why do you think Reyhan took her own life?
你以為雷漢為什麼要結束自己的生命？

555
00:42:43,030 --> 00:42:44,030
F... ck!
該死！

556
00:43:02,470 --> 00:43:03,470
F... ck!
該死！

557
00:43:30,910 --> 00:43:32,310
- Nükhet, hi. - Hi.
-嗨  努赫特-嗨

558
00:43:33,190 --> 00:43:34,630
Did you have a nice sleep?
你睡得好嗎？

559
00:43:35,150 --> 00:43:37,150
Having a rest for about an hour was refreshing.
休息一個小時令人耳目一新

560
00:43:37,990 --> 00:43:39,550
Let's go and have a nice dinner.
我們去吃飯吧

561
00:43:40,390 --> 00:43:42,590
There must be so many things to see here.
這裏一定有很多東西可以參觀

562
00:43:43,470 --> 00:43:44,990
Have you ever been around this way?
你曾經來過這裏嗎？

563
00:43:45,310 --> 00:43:46,310
No, never.
冇有  從冇來過

564
00:43:48,270 --> 00:43:51,550
Look, such an interesting name for a town, Kambura.
你看，這個小鎮的名字真有趣  坎佈拉

565
00:43:52,870 --> 00:43:55,150
Why give such a strange name to the place you live?
為什麼給你居住的地方起這樣一個奇怪的名字？

566
00:43:56,670 --> 00:43:58,990
Maybe, it was others who named it.
也許是別人給它??起的名字

567
00:44:02,590 --> 00:44:03,590
Very interesting.
有意思

568
00:44:05,510 --> 00:44:07,790
-I feel sorry for the residents. -Yes, yes.
-我為居民感到難過-是的

569
00:44:35,990 --> 00:44:37,870
Finally, I got hold of you.
總算聯係到你了

570
00:44:38,190 --> 00:44:40,150
The meeting has only just finished.
會議剛剛結束

571
00:44:40,470 --> 00:44:43,230
How is Ankara? Still hot and dry in the summer?
安卡拉怎麼樣？夏天仍然炎熱幹燥嗎？

572
00:44:43,990 --> 00:44:44,990
It certainly is.
必然是

573
00:44:46,150 --> 00:44:48,350
What is the situation? Did you find anything?
情況如何？你發現了什麼嗎？

574
00:44:48,790 --> 00:44:51,510
I digged into the ministries. But no avail.
我深入各部委，但無濟於事

575
00:44:53,470 --> 00:44:55,230
You will have to cough up some dosh.
得付些錢打點關係

576
00:44:55,670 --> 00:44:57,750
No dosh, I told you it is a favour.
不，我告訴過你這是幫忙

577
00:44:58,630 --> 00:45:02,110
You say favour but asking for the most precious item in the black market.
你說要幫忙，但索要的是黑市中最貴的物品

578
00:45:02,230 --> 00:45:04,710
I have asked million and one people. Nobody knows anything.
我問了很多人  冇人知道

579
00:45:06,150 --> 00:45:07,550
We have to go in reverse order.
我們必須按相反的順序

580
00:45:07,990 --> 00:45:09,110
What do you mean?
你什麼意思？

581
00:45:10,510 --> 00:45:13,870
We'll get in touch with the key people through our contacts.
我們將通過聯係方式與關鍵人員保持聯係

582
00:45:14,110 --> 00:45:15,310
Then we'll make them talk.
那我們就讓他們說話

583
00:45:16,270 --> 00:45:19,430
We are not going to ask who is messing with your case.
我們不會直接問誰在處理你的案件

584
00:45:19,670 --> 00:45:21,070
We'll do the opposite.
我們將相反

585
00:45:21,430 --> 00:45:23,710
We'll bait them with a lot of names...
我們會用很多名字誘餌他們

586
00:45:23,910 --> 00:45:26,870
who supposedly interfering with the case.
誰應該幹預案件

587
00:45:27,190 --> 00:45:29,150
We'll cast the line and wait.
我們就放線等待

588
00:45:29,270 --> 00:45:32,430
- Wait for what? - For bureaucratic ego to take over.
-等待什麼？-讓官僚的自負取而代之

589
00:45:33,310 --> 00:45:37,470
Because whoever is pulling the strings or acting like a middle man...
因為不管是在幕後發號施令的人還是那個看起來像中間人的人……

590
00:45:37,590 --> 00:45:39,550
will get beaten by his ego and begin to talk.
會被他們的自負擊敗並開始交待

591
00:45:39,990 --> 00:45:42,150
He will say "f... ck off, I am the one".
他會說“去尼瑪的，我就是那個人”

592
00:45:42,830 --> 00:45:44,790
This is a long shot. These people are not stupid.
這是個長遠計畫  這些人並不愚蠢

593
00:45:44,990 --> 00:45:46,110
They are stupid.
他們很蠢

594
00:45:46,630 --> 00:45:48,920
The only thing that sets those who wear the same style of suit...
唯一可以讓那些穿著相同西裝的人

595
00:45:48,950 --> 00:45:52,310
apart from one another is to brag about whose back you are scratching.
分崩離析的方法就是吹噓你在給誰走捷徑

596
00:45:54,510 --> 00:45:56,030
You must get really bored in Ankara.
你在安卡拉一定很無聊

597
00:45:57,670 --> 00:46:00,630
It's because it's hot and dry here in the summer.
因為夏天幹熱

598
00:46:18,510 --> 00:46:20,030
You haven't eaten anything.
你什麼都冇吃

599
00:46:21,230 --> 00:46:22,630
I am not hungry mum.
我不餓媽媽

600
00:46:23,070 --> 00:46:24,270
What are you doing?
你在做什麼？

601
00:46:24,630 --> 00:46:26,670
Trying to figure out when everything started and...
試圖弄清事情是什麼時候開始的，

602
00:46:26,790 --> 00:46:28,310
in what order it progressed.
以什麼順序進行

603
00:46:29,630 --> 00:46:30,710
Nevra!
內芙拉！

604
00:46:33,990 --> 00:46:36,390
Have you ever heard a man called Cemil Havran?
你是否聽說過一個叫塞米爾·哈夫蘭的人？

605
00:46:37,710 --> 00:46:40,110
Yes. I even talked to him on the phone the other day.
是的，那天我甚至和他通了電話

606
00:46:40,910 --> 00:46:42,310
He sent his regards to you.
他嚮你緻以問候

607
00:46:44,150 --> 00:46:47,990
I never got around to tell you, thinking they may harm Selim.
我一直冇機會告訴你，認為可能會傷害到塞利姆

608
00:46:49,630 --> 00:46:50,990
Are you still hiding something mum?
你還在隱藏什麼嗎？

609
00:46:51,590 --> 00:46:53,110
Isn't that enough of secrets?
這還不夠秘密嗎？

610
00:46:53,350 --> 00:46:55,950
I am not hiding a secret or anything. I am telling you now.
我冇有隱藏任何秘密，我現在告訴你

611
00:46:56,710 --> 00:46:59,110
Cemil almost owns whole of Kambura.
塞米爾幾乎擁有整個坎佈拉

612
00:47:00,550 --> 00:47:02,950
Nothing ever takes place without his knowledge.
冇有他的話什麼都辦不成

613
00:47:04,270 --> 00:47:06,030
I think you'd better talk to him.
我想你最好和他談談

614
00:47:06,550 --> 00:47:08,950
Was he the one who threatened Uncle Selim?
他是威脅塞利姆叔叔的人嗎？

615
00:47:09,710 --> 00:47:12,990
He wouldn't do it himself. He would get his monkeys do it instead.
他不會自己做，而是要讓他的小弟來做

616
00:47:15,190 --> 00:47:17,270
You know Vural, the guy who's been hanging around.
你認識烏拉爾，一直在閒逛的家夥

617
00:47:18,150 --> 00:47:19,150
Vural.
烏拉爾

618
00:47:19,550 --> 00:47:24,030
Apparently he warned Selim not to talk about the fire.
顯然他警告塞利姆不要說起大火

619
00:47:28,710 --> 00:47:29,830
I see.
我知道了

620
00:47:31,030 --> 00:47:33,190
It means we have to turn Kambura on its head.
這意味著我們必須徹底改變坎佈拉

621
00:47:34,070 --> 00:47:35,510
Don't worry, I'll talk to him.
不用擔心我會跟他談

622
00:47:39,230 --> 00:47:40,630
Mum...
媽

623
00:47:41,710 --> 00:47:43,790
we came here in 1993, didn't we?
我們是1993年來到這裏的，不是嗎？

624
00:47:48,070 --> 00:47:49,270
Stayed here for a year.
在這裏住了一年

625
00:47:52,070 --> 00:47:53,590
1994.
1994年

626
00:47:54,990 --> 00:47:56,750
I think it was August.
我記得是八月

627
00:47:57,190 --> 00:47:59,470
Left in August.
八月離開

628
00:48:02,550 --> 00:48:04,070
Reyhan had a notebook.
雷漢有一個筆記本

629
00:48:06,790 --> 00:48:12,270
If it is as precious as to be hidden under a pillow...
如果它被藏在枕頭下麵

630
00:48:12,350 --> 00:48:13,990
it was more likely a diary.
它更可能是一本日記

631
00:48:14,670 --> 00:48:16,390
Where is that diary now?
那本日記現在在哪裏？

632
00:48:17,070 --> 00:48:20,550
If these notes were taken by Reyhan...
如果這些筆記是雷漢寫的

633
00:48:20,670 --> 00:48:22,950
the killer has the diary.
那麼日記就在兇手那裏

634
00:48:26,950 --> 00:48:29,350
Let's assume that she wrote this on my birthday.
假設她是在我生日那天寫的

635
00:48:32,510 --> 00:48:34,070
March 18th.
3月18日

636
00:48:37,110 --> 00:48:38,510
Nevra...
內芙拉

637
00:48:43,350 --> 00:48:45,750
has Reyhan given you a birthday present?
雷漢給了你生日禮物嗎？

638
00:48:49,030 --> 00:48:50,110
I don't remember.
我不記得了

639
00:48:52,270 --> 00:48:55,110
[It's Nevra's birthday today] [I got her a present].
[今天是內夫拉的生日] [我給她準備了禮物]

640
00:48:58,830 --> 00:49:01,230
- When I set out to write this book... - Life is Traffic.
-當我著手寫這本書時-生活就是交通

641
00:49:02,670 --> 00:49:04,830
I did a lot of research on accidents.
我對事故做了很多研究

642
00:49:07,670 --> 00:49:09,310
- Here you are sir. - Good.
-給你  先生-好

643
00:49:10,950 --> 00:49:13,670
-Go on, open it. -It may cause a problem.
-繼續，打開門。-這可能會引起問題。

644
00:49:14,350 --> 00:49:17,390
The guy himself is the problem. And I am here to solve it.
這個人自己就是問題  我就是解決問題的人

645
00:49:19,030 --> 00:49:20,990
By the way, he won't know about this. Am I clear?
順便說一句，他不會知道的  好嗎？

646
00:49:21,230 --> 00:49:22,230
Yes sir.
是的  先生

647
00:49:38,230 --> 00:49:40,310
There was an incident. I never forget it.
發生了一件事情  我永遠不會忘記

648
00:49:41,510 --> 00:49:44,910
Do you remember the TV show...
你還記得電視節目嗎

649
00:49:45,030 --> 00:49:46,550
the contest...
那個比賽

650
00:49:46,870 --> 00:49:51,030
where contestants gather around a car and place their hands on it.
參賽者聚集在汽車周圍並把手放在汽車上

651
00:49:51,230 --> 00:49:54,070
Yes, I remember it. They used to spend days in that position.
是的，我還記得他們以前在那個位置上度過了好幾天

652
00:49:56,150 --> 00:50:00,190
A man spent 37 hours with his hand on the car.
一個男人把手放在汽車上度過了37個小時

653
00:50:01,070 --> 00:50:04,150
He places his hand on the car and just stands there.
他把手放在車上，站在那裏

654
00:50:04,670 --> 00:50:06,550
He was the one who lasted the longest.
他是曆時最長的人

655
00:50:06,630 --> 00:50:07,950
So, he wins the car.
所以，他贏了車

656
00:50:08,270 --> 00:50:11,230
He takes the car away...
他把車開走了

657
00:50:11,430 --> 00:50:15,710
and on his very first day on the road he gets involved in a horrific accident.
在上路的第一天，他卷入了一場可怕的事故

658
00:50:17,670 --> 00:50:20,710
A truck hits the car on the driver's side.
卡車撞到駕駛員側的轎廂

659
00:50:21,790 --> 00:50:23,630
That is really bad.
真的很糟糕

660
00:50:25,190 --> 00:50:26,470
And there is more.
還有

661
00:50:26,910 --> 00:50:28,350
Do you know what happens?
你知道發生了什麼嗎？

662
00:50:29,310 --> 00:50:34,550
He loses his right hand, the one he used to touch the car for 37 hours.
他失去了右手，那隻他曾經用來摸汽車37小時的右手

663
00:50:38,150 --> 00:50:39,590
Do you think it has a meaning?
你認為這件事含義嗎？

664
00:50:41,550 --> 00:50:43,830
And if there is a meaning, what is it?
如果有含義，那是什麼含義？

665
00:51:17,590 --> 00:51:18,790
Where is that guy now?
那家夥現在在哪裏？

666
00:51:19,230 --> 00:51:20,950
They were talking about having dinner.
他們曾說到晚餐

667
00:51:21,070 --> 00:51:24,150
There is only one place to eat around here which is at the end of the road.
這條路的盡頭隻有一個吃飯的地方

668
00:51:24,230 --> 00:51:25,990
O.K, fine. Thanks.
好，很好

669
00:51:29,270 --> 00:51:31,870
I met a girl today. Her name is Nevra Elmas.
我今天遇到一個女孩，她叫內芙拉·埃爾馬斯

670
00:51:34,830 --> 00:51:38,550
She is the only one I trust. Because Nevra understands me.
她是我唯一信任的人，因為內芙拉了解我

671
00:51:42,470 --> 00:51:45,430
It's Nevra's birthday today. I got her a present.
今天是內夫拉的生日，我給她準備了禮物

672
00:51:51,110 --> 00:51:53,510
Me and Nevra share a secret.
我和費夫拉分享了一個秘密

673
00:51:59,710 --> 00:52:01,150
Did you really kiss?
你真的吻了嗎？

674
00:52:01,710 --> 00:52:03,670
You promised not to tell anyone.
你答應不告訴任何人

675
00:52:04,550 --> 00:52:05,830
Of course we kissed.
我們當然吻了

676
00:52:06,070 --> 00:52:07,150
Swear to God?
嚮上帝發誓？

677
00:52:07,390 --> 00:52:09,990
You don't believe anything. I told you so many times.
你都不相信  我告訴過你很多次

678
00:52:17,830 --> 00:52:21,990
I told Nevra everything. But she doesn't believe me.
我把一切都告訴了內芙拉，但她不相信我

679
00:53:07,310 --> 00:53:08,390
I don't eat fruit.
我不吃水果

680
00:53:08,630 --> 00:53:11,080
Because when the sugar in fruit gets in reaction with alcohol...
因為當水果中的糖與酒精反應時

681
00:53:11,110 --> 00:53:12,550
it turns into fat.
會變成脂肪

682
00:53:27,910 --> 00:53:29,350
Move your hand.
手拿開

683
00:53:38,830 --> 00:53:40,030
Reyhan.
雷漢

684
00:53:40,150 --> 00:53:41,470
Who remembers?
誰記得？

685
00:53:44,310 --> 00:53:45,510
Who remembers?
誰記得？

686
00:53:48,230 --> 00:53:49,230
Tayyar!
塔亞爾！

687
00:53:53,470 --> 00:53:54,870
Tayyar remembers you.
塔亞爾記得你

688
00:53:59,590 --> 00:54:01,790
He said "they wasted the poor girl".
他說：“他們糟蹋了那個可憐的女孩”

689
00:54:06,270 --> 00:54:08,550
If Tayyar remembers so do the others.
如果塔亞爾還記得的話

690
00:54:13,230 --> 00:54:15,630
All of them, they all remember.
他們所有人，他們一定都記得

691
00:54:20,390 --> 00:54:22,030
Whole of Kambura remembers.
整個坎佈拉都記得

692
00:54:23,910 --> 00:54:25,750
They just pretend that they don't.
他們隻是假裝自己不知道

693
00:54:50,990 --> 00:54:52,270
Who am I speaking to?
我在跟誰說話？

694
00:54:53,270 --> 00:54:55,030
Not to your friend in Ankara.
肯定不是在跟你身在安其拉的朋友說話

695
00:54:55,990 --> 00:54:57,230
That's for sure.
這是肯定的

696
00:54:58,070 --> 00:55:00,070
I don't think you should speak to him again either.
我也覺得你不應該再再跟他說話

697
00:55:00,350 --> 00:55:03,110
Save his a..ss and save your own.
救他一命  也救你自己一命

698
00:55:04,310 --> 00:55:06,790
Stick to what you know. Write 3rd page articles.
繼續做你擅長的事情  寫幾頁文章

699
00:55:08,470 --> 00:55:11,270
Because as you turn the pages in a newspaper...
因為當你翻報紙時……

700
00:55:11,390 --> 00:55:13,710
you come to the pages with political issues...
你翻到有關政治問題的頁麵……

701
00:55:13,910 --> 00:55:15,470
and that's where the scenery changes.
那就發生了微妙的變化

702
00:55:15,550 --> 00:55:17,310
You may end up being locked up.
你最後很可能會被關進監獄

703
00:55:18,270 --> 00:55:21,070
And when it comes to trying to prove your innocence...
當你要證明自己無罪的時候……

704
00:55:21,310 --> 00:55:23,350
the trial would last at least a year.
審判將持續至少一年

705
00:55:24,790 --> 00:55:26,190
Have mercy on yourself.
對自己好一點

706
00:55:26,550 --> 00:55:27,630
O.K?
好嗎？

707
00:55:28,270 --> 00:55:31,670
Don't get yourself mixed up with complicated businesses.
不要讓自己與複雜的企業糾纏在一起

708
00:55:31,790 --> 00:55:36,270
Because next time that phone rings, it won't be for a warning.
因為下次電話響起時，不會再警告你

709
00:55:46,950 --> 00:55:48,270
We can leave if you're ready.
如果你準備好了  我們就走吧

710
00:55:53,590 --> 00:55:54,590
This way.
這條路

711
00:56:17,870 --> 00:56:18,870
What is it?
怎麼了？

712
00:56:19,070 --> 00:56:20,590
Police. Don't touch anything.
警察  不要碰任何東西

713
00:56:20,910 --> 00:56:21,910
O.K.
好

714
00:56:38,710 --> 00:56:40,150
We used to drink wine too.
我們以前也喝酒

715
00:56:42,670 --> 00:56:43,670
But the cheapest one.
但是喝最便宜的

716
00:56:44,830 --> 00:56:47,750
It was called the "dog killer". Have you heard of it?
它被稱為“狗殺手”嗎？ 你聽說過嗎？

717
00:56:48,550 --> 00:56:50,510
Do you know what was written on the label?
你知道標簽上寫了什麼嗎？

718
00:56:51,790 --> 00:56:53,230
In vino veritas.
（拉丁語）In vino veritas.

719
00:56:54,630 --> 00:56:55,950
We used to wonder what it meant.
我們以前很想知道這是什麼意思

720
00:56:57,030 --> 00:56:58,030
What does it mean?
這是什麼意思？

721
00:57:01,070 --> 00:57:03,150
The truth is hidden in the wine.
酒醉吐真言

722
00:57:05,350 --> 00:57:07,230
- Leave me alone. - Come on.
-別管我-來吧

723
00:57:07,430 --> 00:57:09,070
- B... stards! - Come on.
-畜生！-走吧

724
00:57:12,350 --> 00:57:14,430
Leave me alone. I can find my own way.
放開我  我自己會走

725
00:57:22,390 --> 00:57:23,910
F... cking gypsy!
該死的吉普賽人！

726
00:57:26,110 --> 00:57:27,630
He's got such a big mouth.
他真是個大嘴巴

727
00:57:28,590 --> 00:57:30,790
He thinks he can take over the place.
他認為他可以接管這個地方

728
00:57:36,150 --> 00:57:37,670
I know you don't like gypsies.
我知道你不喜歡吉普賽人

729
00:57:38,750 --> 00:57:39,950
I f..cking hate them.
我恨死他們了

730
00:57:40,190 --> 00:57:42,790
My dad says they should f... ck off somewhere else.
我爸爸說他們應該滾去別的地方

731
00:57:43,470 --> 00:57:45,750
But saying is not enough Ufuk.
但隻是說說不夠，烏福克

732
00:57:47,030 --> 00:57:48,670
Look how he forces himself on us.
看看他是怎麼強迫我們

733
00:57:49,750 --> 00:57:54,030
Best thing to do is set his bed alight. Let the b... stard burn to ashes.
最好的辦法就是等他上床了，讓那畜生被燒成灰燼

734
00:57:55,350 --> 00:57:57,630
He is a walking alcohol bottle.
他是一個行走的酒瓶

735
00:57:58,390 --> 00:58:00,470
Just one spark would be enough to blow him up.
隻需一點火花就足以點燃他

736
00:58:04,510 --> 00:58:06,150
But we need a hero to do the deed.
但是我們需要一個英雄去行動

737
00:58:08,870 --> 00:58:10,390
Look around you.
看看你周圍

738
00:58:10,950 --> 00:58:14,110
Everybody is sitting all quiet, tails between their legs.
每個人都安靜地坐著  尾巴夾在腿中間

739
00:58:14,350 --> 00:58:16,310
He might've as well spat on their faces.
他還不如往他們臉上吐唾沫呢

740
00:58:17,150 --> 00:58:19,590
We need someone to sort him out.
我們需要一個人來解決他

741
00:58:26,470 --> 00:58:27,550
I'll do it.
我會做的

742
00:58:29,270 --> 00:58:30,830
I swear I can do it.
我發誓我能做到

743
00:58:32,790 --> 00:58:36,390
I will burn that gypsy so bad they will ever dare to return to Kambura.
我將把吉普賽人燒死，讓他們甚至都不敢再回到坎佈拉

744
00:58:37,030 --> 00:58:38,790
Now, this is the man talking.
這才像個男子漢

745
00:58:39,430 --> 00:58:41,630
Come on, bottoms up.
來吧，幹杯

746
00:59:32,790 --> 00:59:33,990
Why are you calling me?
你為什麼給我打電話？

747
00:59:35,190 --> 00:59:37,390
What do you want from me in the middle of the night?
這大半夜的你想要什麼？

748
00:59:39,670 --> 00:59:40,990
Yes, Deva told me.
是的，德瓦告訴我了

749
00:59:43,070 --> 00:59:46,550
O.K, just send the divorce papers. I will sign them.
好，寄離婚文件過來我會簽

750
00:59:47,870 --> 00:59:49,590
What do you mean you changed your mind?
你是什??麼意思  改變主意了？

751
00:59:50,270 --> 00:59:52,230
How can you? Do you think this is a game?
你怎麼可以這樣？你認為這是一個遊戲嗎？

752
00:59:53,750 --> 00:59:55,830
No, I don't want you to come to Turkey.
不，我不要你來土耳其

753
00:59:57,230 --> 00:59:58,870
I have nothing to say to you.
我無話可說

754
01:00:00,430 --> 01:00:03,030
The marriage is over. There is nothing between us.
婚姻結束了  我們之間什麼都冇有

755
01:00:04,030 --> 01:00:05,430
Don't ever call me again.
永遠不要再打給我

756
01:00:31,430 --> 01:00:32,800
Who was it, calling this time at night?
是誰，這麼晚了打電話？

757
01:00:32,830 --> 01:00:33,830
Deva.
德瓦

758
01:00:34,150 --> 01:00:37,110
He was looking for something but couldn't find it.
他在找東西，但找不到

759
01:00:37,310 --> 01:00:38,510
Called to ask me.
打電話問我

760
01:00:57,630 --> 01:00:58,830
I don't think he found it.
我覺得他還是冇找到

761
01:01:00,670 --> 01:01:01,790
I'll be right back.
我馬上回來

762
01:01:18,910 --> 01:01:22,750
- Thank you very much Nükhet. - What for?
-非常感謝  努赫特-謝我什麼？

763
01:01:24,910 --> 01:01:28,870
I haven't felt this peaceful for ages.
我好久冇有感到這種平靜了

764
01:01:33,990 --> 01:01:35,390
And you are the reason.
而你就是原因

765
01:01:37,470 --> 01:01:39,550
I feel like I am going to live forever.
我覺得我能長生不老了

766
01:01:41,950 --> 01:01:47,070
I feel like me and you will be sitting here, watching the stars forever.
我感覺就像我和你你將永遠坐在這裏，看星星

767
01:01:49,670 --> 01:01:51,110
As if it will never end.
仿佛永遠不會結束

768
01:01:54,150 --> 01:01:55,590
It will not end Agah.
不會結束的  阿加

769
01:01:56,790 --> 01:01:59,950
We will relive tonight every time we think about it.
我們每次想到這裏時都可以將這個夜晚重溫

770
01:02:01,270 --> 01:02:02,590
Under the stars.
星空下

771
01:02:05,390 --> 01:02:06,630
As long as we remember.
隻要我們記得

772
01:02:08,910 --> 01:02:10,630
That's what the poet said.
那是詩人所說的

773
01:02:11,830 --> 01:02:15,670
Life is a memory. You'll die when you forget.
生命是一種回憶  你忘記了就會死

774
01:02:17,310 --> 01:02:19,150
So true. Who said it?
還真是這樣，是誰說的？

775
01:02:21,790 --> 01:02:22,790
I forgot.
我忘了

776
01:02:40,990 --> 01:02:41,990
I washed him.
我洗了他

777
01:02:44,190 --> 01:02:45,350
Sure I washed him.
我很肯定我洗了

778
01:02:47,310 --> 01:02:50,910
I washed Tufan. They can't find any evidence.
我洗了圖凡的屍體  他們找不到任何證據

779
01:02:53,750 --> 01:02:55,510
I remembered. See?
我記得的  你看？

780
01:02:57,470 --> 01:03:00,830
You dirty crooks. I washed him.
你這骯髒的騙子  我洗了他

781
01:03:04,790 --> 01:03:07,070
Well, now that I am awake...!
好吧，現在我醒過來了……！

782
01:03:51,950 --> 01:03:54,230
It's not here. How could you forget it?
不在這裏，怎麼會忘記呢？

783
01:03:55,550 --> 01:03:56,630
How could you forget it?
你怎麼會忘記帶槍？

784
01:07:00,910 --> 01:07:02,670
Wait here. I'll be right back.
在這裏等我  我馬上回來

785
01:07:18,590 --> 01:07:20,910
- Where have you been? - I am here aren't I?
-你去哪裏了？-我現在來了  不是嗎？

786
01:07:21,750 --> 01:07:23,910
Did you tell your dad that we are going to get married?
你有冇有告訴你父親我們要結婚了？

787
01:07:24,990 --> 01:07:27,670
No, I didn't have the chance. But I have something else to tell you.
不，我還冇有機會，但我還有其他事情要告訴你

788
01:07:31,950 --> 01:07:33,830
Remember I told you I have a brother? Cemil.
還記得我告訴過你我有一個兄弟嗎？塞米爾

789
01:07:34,150 --> 01:07:35,470
Yes, that's the one.
是的  我知道

790
01:07:35,910 --> 01:07:39,270
He said "now that Reyhan kissed you, would she kiss me too".
他說：“現在雷漢已經吻了你，她會吻我嗎？”

791
01:07:39,510 --> 01:07:40,590
What are you talking about?
你在說什麼？

792
01:07:40,710 --> 01:07:41,910
Wait.
等等

793
01:07:43,110 --> 01:07:45,600
He said he will tell everybody, people will be calling you names...
他說他會告訴所有人，人們都將知道你的名字

794
01:07:45,630 --> 01:07:47,270
and we won't be able to get married.
我們就不能結婚了

795
01:07:57,470 --> 01:07:58,470
Hello Reyhan.
你好  雷漢

796
01:08:00,630 --> 01:08:01,630
How are you?
你好嗎？

797
01:08:30,870 --> 01:08:32,750
What's going on here so early in the morning?
大清早的這是怎麼回事？

798
01:08:44,510 --> 01:08:49,190
[Do you remember me?]
[你還記得我嗎？]

